00:26:21.496 --> 00:26:25.500 line:90% position:50% align:center
Brother Grim has been appointed
to serve on the Branch Committee.

00:26:33.775 --> 00:26:38.179 line:90% position:50% align:center
Brother Kitts has been assigned
to the Central Europe branch,

00:26:38.179 --> 00:26:40.282 line:90% position:50% align:center
where he will work under the oversight

00:26:40.282 --> 00:26:44.486 line:90% position:50% align:center
of World Headquarters Office
