00:27:04.873 --> 00:27:07.375 line:90% position:50% align:center
Brother and Sister Peltonen
have been assigned

00:27:07.375 --> 00:27:09.911 line:90% position:50% align:center
to the Central Europe branch.

00:27:09.911 --> 00:27:12.881 line:90% position:50% align:center
Brother Peltonen
will work under the oversight

00:27:12.881 --> 00:27:17.152 line:90% position:50% align:center
of World Headquarters Office
